              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fillRule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clipRule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Blog corporativo integrado</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-cyan/10 to-blue-500/10 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-cyan/20">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">Portafolios Creativos</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
              Showcase visual para diseñadores, fotógrafos, arquitectos y profesionales creativos.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-cyan mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fillRule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clipRule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Galerías de proyectos optimizadas</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-cyan mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fillRule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clipRule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Carga lazy de imágenes HD</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-cyan mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fillRule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clipRule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Filtros por categoría y tags</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-purple/10 to-violet-500/10 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-purple/20">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">Sitios Institucionales</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
              Plataformas para ONGs, fundaciones y organizaciones sin fines de lucro.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fillRule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clipRule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Sección de noticias y eventos</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fillRule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clipRule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Integración con donaciones</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fillRule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clipRule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Multiidioma opcional</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-cyan/10 to-blue-500/10 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-cyan/20">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">Blogs Profesionales</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
              Plataformas de contenido para expertos, influencers y creadores de contenido.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-cyan mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fillRule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clipRule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Editor de contenido avanzado</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
